<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Semigroups on Chen Kai Blog</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/semigroups/</link><description>Recent content in Semigroups on Chen Kai Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Oct 2021 09:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/semigroups/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>泛函分析（十）：算子半群——无穷维的演化方程</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/functional-analysis/10-%E7%AE%97%E5%AD%90%E5%8D%8A%E7%BE%A4/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 Oct 2021 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.chenk.top/zh/functional-analysis/10-%E7%AE%97%E5%AD%90%E5%8D%8A%E7%BE%A4/</guid><description>&lt;p>考虑最简单的常微分方程：&lt;span class="math-inline">$u&amp;#39;(t) = au(t)$&lt;/span>
，&lt;span class="math-inline">$u(0) = u_0$&lt;/span>
，其中 &lt;span class="math-inline">$a$&lt;/span>
 是实数。解为 &lt;span class="math-inline">$u(t) = e^{at}u_0$&lt;/span>
。映射族 &lt;span class="math-inline">$T(t): u_0 \mapsto e^{at}u_0$&lt;/span>
 构成单参数群，满足 &lt;span class="math-inline">$T(0) = I$&lt;/span>
，&lt;span class="math-inline">$T(t&amp;#43;s) = T(t)T(s)$&lt;/span>
，且当 &lt;span class="math-inline">$t \to 0$&lt;/span>
 时 &lt;span class="math-inline">$T(t) \to I$&lt;/span>
。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>现在用 Banach 空间 &lt;span class="math-inline">$X$&lt;/span>
 上的有界算子 &lt;span class="math-inline">$A$&lt;/span>
 取代标量 &lt;span class="math-inline">$a$&lt;/span>
。指数 &lt;span class="math-inline">$e^{tA} = \sum_{n=0}^\infty (tA)^n / n!$&lt;/span>
 在算子范数下收敛，&lt;span class="math-inline">$T(t) = e^{tA}$&lt;/span>
 求解抽象 Cauchy 问题 &lt;span class="math-inline">$u&amp;#39;(t) = Au(t)$&lt;/span>
。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>